descriptionHtml:
this is my attempt to make a pretty Jenassa. i wanted to marry a dark elf, but i got tired of lookin\' at her. gave her a bluer shade and her tattoo, changed her lips, and gave her the unique dark elf eyes. this mod also makes her start with elven armor and glass weapons.

not required but HIGHLY recommended

Smoothed Dunmer by Xenius
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=30

this removes the big eye brow bone structure dunmer have.

optional:
Covereyes by mrLenski
